Who is Sam?

Hey guys and girls. I am Sam and this website will be about me!

The first thing you will probably ask yourself is "Who is Sam?". Well, I am a graduate from University College London, who is currently undertaking training in Software development. Apart from that, I am a sport enthusiast who plays football. I also watch football and I am an Arsenal fan. If you like what you're reading, then please read more.

In this website, I will be giving you guys a gerneral description of me and I will also be posting some of my projects that I have been working on as well.
